node.text: Getting ready to do a whole bunch of nothing lol. Definitely going to make some of these makeup items everyday staples 🤗

Here we have it, folks! My “flawless dewy skin routine” with my favorite @Dermstore products. I have been choosing to shop at @dermstore for a while now for my go-to beauty brands. Enter my giveaway to win up to $1,000 of my favorite @dermstore products & let’s have some on fleek skin together, wooo! 🌟
